  "name": "Morrison CFD Hemolysis Credibility Assessment — CPB Pump (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "Credibility assessment for CFD-based hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump intended for cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) use at Model Risk Level 2. The model is used to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device. All 7 assessed credibility factors meet required levels; 6 factors are scoped out as acceptable at MRL 2. Decision: Accepted. Intended use scope is described in the Requirement and Claim nodes bound below.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-mrl2",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cpb-cfd-hemolysis-worst-case",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-generic-centrifugal-pump-cfd-v2",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-experimental-hemolysis-dataset",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-piv-velocity-dataset"
  ],
